Description
PT Valve Automation Indonesia (VAI) business mainly to provide top works facilities for ESD/SDV, Blowdown valve, Motorized valve and automated control valve for Oil & Gas, Petrochemical, Power Plant & Pulp & Paper industry. To support fast delivery, PT VAI keep stock for the Actuator & it’s accessories such as ASCO Solenoid valve, Filter Regulator, STONEL Limit Switch and etc, in one roof concept which including the assembling facility for valve automation with the latest technology in the market. VAI is Appointed Agent covering Indonesia Oil and Gas Region for CCI Control Valve, ROTORK Actuator, ASCO Solenoid Valve & STONEL Limit Switch.
Job Description :
Aid marketing team in qualifying new markets and application areas Perform as technical lead in new applications development as well as interfacing with the customer Assist in development of new products, product configurations and process analyzers that matches with customer applications Assist sales team on developing new sales channels, sales leads and closing sales Other marketing/sales activities related to the above job descriptions
Requirements
Will be a graduate from one of the leading universities who possesses chemistry, physics or related degrees at BS/MS levels  Minimum of 3 years of industrial experience in the field of analytical chemistry, analytical instrumentations and/or industrial process engineering involving sensors/transducers integration.  Experience in process gas analysers and its related sample handling system is required. Basic knowledge in spectroscopy or any other analyser technology platform is a plus. Familiarity with two or more of the following analysers:
Optical Spectroscopy/ (UV/IR/NIR/NDIR/TDL) Process Gas Chromatographs             TCD         Oxygen Analysers             CEMS             Calorimeter             Fire & Gas Detection             Other Gas Analyzers with other technology platforms
Good understanding of process control, hardware integration, plumbing and piping in chemical plants and manufacturing environments Some Experience in process sensors/transducers, automated valves for process control and PLC control system is a plus Good written and verbal communication skills. Fluent in English language – conversational, writing and listening. Willingness to learn New Technologies & Applications Has an appetite for start-ups environments and can thrive in such challenging & rewarding conditions
All applications will be treated confidentially & only short listed candidates will be notified
